The paper proposes a mutation testing framework specialized for DL systems to measure the quality of test data. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) category. However, the paper also focuses on DL models and their training data, which suggests that it could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) categories.
